Amanda Holden, 51, took to Instagram today to share an update with her 1.8 million followers. The Britain’s Got Talent judge put her long, toned pins on show in a mini skirt and blazer co-ord while she posed for the camera. Leaning against a table, Amanda kicked her leg up in a fun Boomerang post and a snap uploaded to her main feed. Fans of the TV star rushed to the post’s comments section to heap praise on the blonde beauty’s ageless appearance. Hicsqueak said: “You’re gorgeous, star.” Michaelelse8 added: “Sensational legs Mandy. Body of a 20 year old.” While Hornetbiker86 penned: “Legs to die for.”